snippet.title: Feisty Fauna gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Feisty Fauna is a ridiculously cute survivors-like / bullet heaven where you're an animal trying to survive. Whether it's by laying traps, being a ninja, or charming minions, you will hunt other cute animals in this eat-or-be-eaten animal world.

Play the demo and wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1916560/Feisty_Fauna/
